Description: Stub package for the Gurobi Optimizer R interface.
    The full 'gurobi' R package is distributed by Gurobi Optimization
    (<https://www.gurobi.com/>) and requires a Gurobi license.
    This stub exists so that packages listing 'gurobi' in Enhances
    can pass CRAN checks. Install the real package from Gurobi.
